flowchart LR
  UI[Task detail route /tasks/:taskId] --> URL[URL state parser]
  URL --> CLIENT[Task detail API client]
  CLIENT --> DETAIL[/GET /tasks/:id/detail/]
  CLIENT --> SUMMARY[/GET /tasks/:id/]
  CLIENT --> HISTORY[/GET /tasks/:id/history/]
  CLIENT --> TELEMETRY[/GET /tasks/:id/observability-summary/]

  DETAIL --> HTTP[Audit HTTP layer]
  SUMMARY --> HTTP
  HISTORY --> HTTP
  TELEMETRY --> HTTP

  HTTP --> STATE[(audit_task_current_state)]
  HTTP --> HISTORY_PROJ[(audit_task_history)]
  HTTP --> REL[(audit_task_relationships)]
  HTTP --> OBS[(structured observability summary)]

  HTTP --> VM[Detail view-model composer]
  STATE --> VM
  HISTORY_PROJ --> VM
  REL --> VM
  OBS --> VM

  VM --> DETAIL
  HISTORY --> UI
  TELEMETRY --> UI
  DETAIL --> UI
